{"tid":717600,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[濕疹] 醫生要我戒味精/濃味野，出街食既話有咩選擇 ?_?","createTime":"2018-06-26T07:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T01:54:31.000Z","uid":53349,"like":25,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"781dd43e82286522931dc6536a32084fedb6b342","tid":717600,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"我初初都唔信，但時間耐左，少左出街食又真係好好多，一出街食又出事。<br />\n<br />\n一直lunch都係屋企煮，但近排見皮膚好返少少，就想出去做運動，懶得煮，唔想洗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次出街都係咬唐記饅頭，諗唔到有咩好揀，又想轉下口味，一路試唔同餐廳，次次都出事咁濟，試到驚所以上黎求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得問題不大，我又唔係好介意餐餐饅頭，不過如果有得揀都想轉下咁姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3143c8dbc00c0b2f4d643eb8a06e8e053abb240a","tid":717600,"uid":4550,"like":111,"dislike":18,"score":93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:16:39.000Z","msg":"大快活雞胸紅米飯"},{"pid":"b727d75ecae5d745c079c62b672ef2d6f3970bc1","tid":717600,"uid":9115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:17:43.000Z","msg":"咁叫醫好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62265bfe338aa4f315771535abddf95e6c563cfc","tid":717600,"uid":90023,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"3143c8dbc00c0b2f4d643eb8a06e8e053abb240a","tid":717600,"uid":4550,"like":111,"dislike":18,"score":93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:16:39.000Z","msg":"大快活雞胸紅米飯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"重點 係 走汁"},{"pid":"b20391339bcdfb401b60681f56fe16c723134319","tid":717600,"uid":53349,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b727d75ecae5d745c079c62b672ef2d6f3970bc1","tid":717600,"uid":9115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:17:43.000Z","msg":"咁叫醫好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"我未好既，係最近舒服啲姐，醫生話等到好哂就可以正常人咁飲食。不過我都係半信半疑，可能好返都要繼續咁戒，但我濕疹咁耐得呢個方法最有效，唯有跟佢講咁戒住先<br />\n<br />\n每個個案都唔同，可能係我呢個case閪啲要咁戒姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：天生濕疹+腸胃差"},{"pid":"8939ac781f605dae305af4a992e4e8fd2a488825","tid":717600,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3143c8dbc00c0b2f4d643eb8a06e8e053abb240a","tid":717600,"uid":4550,"like":111,"dislike":18,"score":93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:16:39.000Z","msg":"大快活雞胸紅米飯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121ba7c143c27df168426e009d82d6b984124288","tid":717600,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"62265bfe338aa4f315771535abddf95e6c563cfc","tid":717600,"uid":90023,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"3143c8dbc00c0b2f4d643eb8a06e8e053abb240a","tid":717600,"uid":4550,"like":111,"dislike":18,"score":93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:16:39.000Z","msg":"大快活雞胸紅米飯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:19:18.000Z","msg":"重點 係 走汁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:24:56.000Z","msg":"marked<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edda914c59ade1fa695474505a2116b6c997771d","tid":717600,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"M記"},{"pid":"a47d95f88095b32a57ad1a7af1f7cb2dc7cc15a2","tid":717600,"uid":102850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:27:29.000Z","msg":"身同感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b93d229775c84ffd744b15f9fd07165d823e1f","tid":717600,"uid":77484,"like":148,"dislike":2,"score":146,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:28:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f734f3a84dad8d5acf3ed493000e