唔用精調味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8472ac07e51295bb05e4d605e96ac022a311ae52","tid":717600,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:39:04.000Z","msg":"戒口似乎對濕疹唔一定有幫助<br />\n又或者濕疹唔似因為食物引起<br />\n因為有病人話我知，佢屋企人細個無，係大個先有，仲驗到係鰻魚引起<br />\n無理由細個食無事，大個食有事<br />\n錯不在鰻魚，問題只係身體有改變，引起濕疹，鰻魚只係咁岩trigger到"},{"pid":"c384112912d8796f325bdef645183306c7c73b0e","tid":717600,"uid":99734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:40:12.000Z","msg":"我以前都係咁 <br />\n而家斷左尾 完全無戒口都無野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人經驗 唔洗戒到咁足 盡量食豬 魚 菜 以蒸為主"},{"pid":"1454a686b30be5d740623376dd691f0af8f3bfe0","tid":717600,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44c783f5ba79273d50adeefaa09d844af071c81b","tid":717600,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64acb2e76048999f2d3700ddd6a130730a74159a","tid":717600,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"986384080f1eedb448247d27cc82bba17dbcd075","tid":717600,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:28:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://celiac.org/celiac-disease/understanding-celiac-disease-2/non-celiac-gluten-sensitivity-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fceliac.org%2Fceliac-disease%2Funderstanding-celiac-disease-2%2Fnon-celiac-gluten-sensitivity-2%2F&d=AUEgvheeUj78fjgBelS1%2FkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6abde78a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://celiac.org/celiac-disease/understanding-celiac-disease-2/non-celiac-gluten-sensitivity-2/</a><br />\n<br />\nyw"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"咁重係咪濕疹。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:37:19.000Z","msg":"gluten free diet dermatitis herpetiformis<br />\n<br />\ngoogle it"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:41:56.000Z","msg":"You win <img src=\"/a